org.smtlib

Class IVisitor.TreeVisitor<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.smtlib.IVisitor.TreeVisitor<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the return value
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IVisitor<T>
    Enclosing interface:
    IVisitor<T>

    public static class IVisitor.TreeVisitor<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IVisitor<T>
    This class is an implementation of IVisitor meant fur further derivation: each visitor is implemented to visit its children without doing anything else; the default return value is null.
